==Career== In 1995, Suneetha starred in the [[Arifa Ibrahim]]-directed family drama ''[[Manzil (1995 film)|Manzil]]'' (1995) which follows as an intelligent and hardworking orphan, whose life takes a dramatic turn while working as a servant in a reputed family.<ref name=ShameelInt>{{cite news|url=https://www.muniavas.com/21829 |title=Shameel to play a tough father's role in Hanaa |work=MuniAvas |language=Divehi |last=Rasheed |first=Ahmed |date=9 January 2020 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201029145929/https://www.muniavas.com/21829 |url-status=live |archivedate=29 October 2020 |accessdate=29 October 2020}}</ref>
