8/04/local-news/garnier-miadhu-crystal-award-night-yousey-afee-and-chiliya-bags-top-awards-6169/ |url-status=dead |archive-date=4 January 2014 |access-date=5 December 2020}}</ref> |- | Best Video Song | "Crazy Khiyaaley" - ''Hiyy Dheewaanaa 4'' | {{won}} |style="text-align:center;"|<ref name=2ndMiadhuCrystal/> |- | Best Choreography | "Crazy Khiyaaley" - ''Hiyy Dheewaanaa 4'' | {{won}} |style="text-align:center;"|<ref name=2ndMiadhuCrystal/> |- | 2021 ! scope="row" | ASIA Awards 2020/2021 | colspan="2"| Asia's Outstanding Woman Achiever Award | {{won}} |style="text-align:center;"| <ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.asiaawards.org/news/suneetha-ali-has-bagged-asia's-outstanding-woman-achiever-award |title=Suneetha Ali has bagged Asia's Outstanding Woman Achiever Award |work=Asia Awards |date=7 December 2021 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20220107032723/https://www.asiaawards.org/ |url-status= live |archivedate=7 January 2022 |accessdate=7 January 2022 |df=dmy-all}}</ref> |- | 2021 ! scope="row" | Women Icon Award 2021 | colspan="2"| Outstanding Women Award | {{won}} |style="text-align:center;"| <ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.muniavas.com/39444 |title=Another International Award for Sunee |language=Divehi |work=MuniAvas |last=Rasheed |first=Ahmed |date=27 December 2021 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20220107033111/https://www.muniavas.com/39444 |url-status= live |archivedate=7 January 2022 |accessdate=7 January 2022 |df=dmy-all}}</ref> |- |}
